examples.en: Seth was tormented by feelings of guilt.
The disease has tormented me for sixteen years.
examples.ru: Эта болезнь мучила меня в течение шестнадцати лет.

examples.en: The children tormented the stuttering teacher.
The sinners will be tormented in Hell, according to the Bible.
examples.ru: Согласно библии, грешники будут мучиться в аду.
